{"tid":656847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"修女性侵男童後懷孕 受害人與親生女重逢","createTime":"2018-05-07T14:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T17:13:55.000Z","uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"29d5b7ffb6d1fa304b2c5611fb0f861b41adcbd0","tid":656847,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"事主Edward Hayes 10歲時因為家貧而入住由教會開設的收容所，有飯吃、有人照料、成為高材生，Edward以為人生出現曙光，殊不知竟是黑暗的序幕&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n27歲的愛爾蘭籍修女Mary Conleth來到收容所，負責洗衣工作，並找Edward幫忙。二人經常獨處一室。<br />\n <br />\n不久，Mary修女就開始侵犯Edward。之後Edward更獲破格安排入住單人房，可是夜晚關燈後，Mary修女便會走入他的房間&hellip;&hellip;這樣的事情發生了3年，直到Mary修女因為懷孕而返回愛爾蘭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BF%AE%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E5%BE%8C%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95-%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA60%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E8%88%87%E8%A6%AA%E7%94%9F%E5%A5%B3%E9%87%8D%E9%80%A2-061512711.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25AD%2595-%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA60%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2580%25A2-061512711.html&d=YMKMvWjbSZ2l7e2QC27ucv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=31a51e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BF%AE%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E5%BE%8C%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95-%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA60%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E8%88%87%E8%A6%AA%E7%94%9F%E5%A5%B3%E9%87%8D%E9%80%A2-061512711.html</a>"},{"pid":"52d8e1870611dfbd1fc6f728272c60429c8f40d3","tid":656847,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e94439679ea6d14614ba3e3b44896ba1e76bf6","tid":656847,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r